a.title: ― TemporalRelation: Set of thirteen Allen's interval relations defined as Contains, Finishes, Meets, Overlaps, Precedes, Starts (and their converses), plus Equals. These are jointly exhaustive and pairwise disjoint binary relations representing temporal relationships between pairs of time intervals.
